# Formspree form ID — create a form at https://formspree.io and paste its ID here.
# Three things POST to https://formspree.io/f/<ID>: the contact form, the
# fish-platter order builder, and the fresh-fish e-mail notifier (each sets a
# `form` field so submissions can be told apart in the Formspree inbox).
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ID=YOUR_FORMSPREE_ID
